      • go

        public Room go(java.lang.String direction)
        Return the room located in the specified direction. If there is no room in the specified direction, displays a message in the console and returns the current room.
        Parameters:
        direction - the direction of the room you want to go compared to this room.
        Returns:
        the room located in the specified direction if it exists, the current room otherwise.
